title: Python package for macOS missing.
body_html:
The python 3 gpu package listed on: https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_mac#the_url_of_the_tensorflow_python_package is missing.

$ curl https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/mac/gpu/tensorflow_gpu-1.1.0-py3-none-any.whl
<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><Error><Code>NoSuchKey</Code><Message>The specified key does not exist.</Message></Error>
body_text: The python 3 gpu package listed on: https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_mac#the_url_of_the_tensorflow_python_package is missing. $ curl https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/mac/gpu/tensorflow_gpu-1.1.0-py3-none-any.whl NoSuchKeyThe specified key does not exist.
